1. *Rado* ću da ti pomognem. (I gladly will help you.)
2. *Rada* bih da se družimo. (I would like to hang out.)
3. *Rado* ćeš videti najbolji ishod. (You will gladly see the best outcome.)
4. *Radovao* se njenom uspehu. (He was delighted with her success.)
5. *Radovala* se što je dobila lep dar. (She was happy that she received a nice gift.)